headline: US Bancorp: Despite Rate Risk, Series A Preferred Still A Good Buy
summary: US Bancorp's Series A preferred shares offer a stable 7% yield despite interest rate fluctuations, backed by improved net interest income and what appears to be a secure common dividend.
